      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOUTH AUSSIE STAR (2) ran fourth last start at this track over 1800m, beaten 9 metres. Talented and has plenty of upside. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position and she is good enough to fight out the finish. IDEAL MIKI (1) is stepping out for the first time. By Always B Miki and hails from the Trevor Patching stable. Has the benefit of a good draw and has the right credentials to play a major role. FARROH GODDESS (4) lines up for the first time. By Century Farroh and hails from the Dale Afford stable. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to her career. OUR PRINCESS HONEY (3) is a two-year-old filly from the D Girardi stable on debut. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw and will be ready to run a big race.",
